"{\"uid\": \"devdiscourse.com-article-entertainment-3035257-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony-outrage-takes-legal-turn\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"A legal battle has erupted following the Paris Olympics' opening ceremony outrage, involving DJ Barbara Butch, a prominent LGBTQ+ figure.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 137, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 96, \"end\": 109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"score\": 0.9999897744159937, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Barbara Butch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Butch has faced severe online abuse including death threats, torture, and rape threats, along with anti-Semitic, homophobic, and sexist slurs.\", \"from\": 138, \"to\": 280, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 237, \"end\": 249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antisemitism\", \"score\": 0.9998949108983418, \"rank\": 0.00010510010352155207, \"text\": \"anti-Semitic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antisemitism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antisemitism\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Butch's controversial performance, which some critics claimed mocked Leonardo Da Vinci's 'The Last Supper', was defended by artistic director Thomas Jolly and event organizers as a celebration of community tolerance and diversity.\", \"from\": 282, \"to\": 512, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 351, \"end\": 359, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 0.9999956383735102, \"rank\": 4.361645421588266e-06, \"text\": \"Leonardo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}, {\"begin\": 360, \"end\": 368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.326633821568384e-17, \"text\": \"Da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}, {\"begin\": 424, \"end\": 430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarence_Thomas\", \"score\": 0.9736232934423159, \"rank\": 0.026944653737306815, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarence_Thomas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarence_Thomas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Butch wore a silver halo-inspired headdress and was joined by drag artists and dancers.\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 600, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the backlash, Butch remains resolute, stating her pride in her performance.\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 685, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Legal complaints will target both French and international perpetrators of the harassment.\", \"from\": 686, \"to\": 776, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Butch and her lawyer are determined to hold those responsible accountable, emphasizing her commitment to inclusivity and love.\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 903, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"(With inputs from agencies.)\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 933, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Email: info@devdiscourse.comPhone: +91-720-6444012, +91-7027739813, 14, 15  \\u00a9 Copyright 2025\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 1027, \"entities\": []}]}"